1949;;A Boy, a Girl and a Bike;;British;;Ralph Smart;;John McCallum, Honor Blackman;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Boy,_a_Girl_and_a_Bike;;Young couple Sue (Honor Blackman) and Sam (Patrick Holt) are members of a Yorkshire cycling club, the ‘Wakeford Wheelers’. Romantic complications ensue when wealthy David (John McCallum) becomes smitten with Sue, and joins the club to pursue her, much to Sam's dismay.